https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51348919/couldnt-process-file-resx-due-to-its-being-in-the-internet-or-restricted-zone-o    Open the file explorer. Navigate to project/solution directory    Search for *.resx. --> You will get list of resx files    Right click the resx file, open the properties and check the option 'Unblock'    Repeat #3 for each resx file.    Reload the project.https://superuser.com/q/44503None of these answers worked for me, I had to do the following:    Start Menu > type 'Internet Options'.    Select Local intranet zone on the Security tab then click the Sites button    Click Advanced button    Enter file://[computer name]    Make sure 'Require server verification...' is unticked